</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-68_ pf-text-1">Supervise children closely around pets and unfamiliar animals.




















</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-70_ pf-text-1">Ensure pets are vaccinated and receive regular health check-ups.





















